Name: nyt-docket
Version: 0.0.4
Summary: Python client for parsing SCOTUS cases from the granted/noted and orders dockets.
Home-page: https://github.com/newsdev/nyt-docket
Author: Jeremy Bowers
Author-email: jeremy.bowers@nytimes.com
